{
  "style": "",
  "texts": [
    "A preliminary experiment is conducted to evaluate the accuracy of the OASST reward model on the JCM dataset.",
    "The paired entries in the JCM dataset are used, where one of the entries is positive (incorrect) and the other is negative (not incorrect).",
    "The sentences are input into the reward model, and the accuracy is computed by the ratio of paired entries with the negative entry having a higher reward score than the positive entry.",
    "Paired entries with the same labels are discarded for this experiment.",
    "The OASST reward model achieves an accuracy of 0.692 on the JCM dataset."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}